ed wood and broken rafterOn the side of lake and river--  By Ever Smart. Translated by Ever Smart天地方寸，荡气回肠。-- Ever Smart The tiny picture contain heaven and earth，Infinite soul stirring arousedThe withered wood and broken rafterOn the side of lake and river--  By Ever Smart. Translated by Ever SmartA cold sun casting its shadowOver frozen waterIce crystals clinging to the belly of a weathered old dockLike young ones suckling at mother's teats-- ThomasA cold sun casting its shadow静湖枯木冰柱，凡夫见到麻木。色彩光影构图，美轮美奂超俗。-- 晓萍静湖枯木冰柱，凡夫见到麻木。色彩光影构图，美轮美奂超俗。-- 晓萍落日溶金，枯木逄春。如歌如画，美照永恒。-- Ever SmartThe sunset like the melting goldThe withered wood get a new lease on lifeThe picturesque landscape as a song The beautiful pictures  become eternal--  By Ever Smart. Translated by Ever Smart落日溶金，枯木逄春。如歌如画，美照永恒。-- Ever SmartThe sunset like the melting goldThe withered wood get a new lease on life你也曾茂密过，也曾被鲜花果实包围过，如今却被苍凉孤独取代了……但我却要赞美你，以死亡的躯体与湖畔一起完成了复活！枯木逢春固然惊喜，但如不能再创辉煌，也有静静存在的理由和乐趣……-- 金锦你也曾茂密过，也曾被鲜花果实包围过，如今却被苍凉孤独取代了……但我却要赞美你，以死亡的躯体与湖畔一起完成了复活！枯木逢春固然惊喜，但如不能再创辉煌，也有静静存在的理由和乐趣……-- 金锦谢谢欣赏谢谢欣赏